| Low-Density Lipoprotein (LDL-C) | 低密度脂蛋白 | 70 - 130 | mg/dL | High: >130 |
| Neutral Fat (MB) | 中性脂肪 | 3.5 - 5.2 | mmol/L | High: >5.2, Low: <3.5 |
| Circulating Immune Complex (CIC) | 循环免疫复合物 | 1.5 - 4.0 | μg/mL | High: >4.0, Low: <1.5 |

